de.learnlib.algorithms.lstargeneric.table

Class Inconsistency<I,O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.learnlib.algorithms.lstargeneric.table.Inconsistency<I,O>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - input symbol class
    O - output class

    public final class Inconsistency<I,O>
extends Object
    A description of an inconsistency in an ObservationTable. An inconsistency consists of two short prefixes u, u' with identical contents, and an input symbol a, such that the rows for ua and u'a have different contents.
    Author:
    Malte Isberner
